overview: Wrestle Queendom is coming up on May 5th , and women's wrestling fans have a lot to be excited about. It is the largest women's wrestling event ever held in Europe, and the card is an incredible mix of international superstars and home grown talent. Luckily, international fans are going to be able to watch the action live thanks to Fite TV. There is literally no better time to get into the world of Pro Wrestling EVE.
title: EVE #SHEVOLUTION
